武汉新增病例何时“清零”？李兰娟回应。
When did Wuhan add new cases "Qingnil"? Li Lanjuan responded.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
张意轩、王坎、王翔宇、乔外/人民日报客户端在湖北武汉，中国工程院院士、国家卫健委高级别专家组成员李兰娟接受了人民日报的专访。
Zhang Yixuan, Wang Kan, Wang Xiangyu, Qiao Xiangyu, Qiao outside / People's Daily clients in Hubei Wuhan, China Academy of Engineering academician, high-level expert group member Li Lanjuan gave an interview to the People's Daily.
武汉新增病例何时“清零”？如何看待当前的抗“疫”形势？新冠疫情会不会在全球更大范围内爆发？这些热点问题，李兰娟都有回应，一起来看：武汉进入决胜阶段，要“穷追猛打”武汉市的疫情防控进入了决胜阶段，现在决不能放松，一定要“穷追猛打”，把所有传染源彻底找出来。
Wuhan when the new cases "clear zero"? How to look at the current situation of "epidemic"? Wuhan into the decisive stage, to "catch up" Wuhan into the decisive phase of the epidemic prevention and control of Wuhan into the decisive phase, must not relax, must "pursue vigorously" and find all sources of infection thoroughly.
只有（医院）外面的感染者都“清零”了，我们才能说武汉安全了。
Only outside the infected people are "clean", we can say Wuhan is safe.
武汉新增病例有望三月底“清零”武汉何时“清零”，归根到底要看我们的工作力度。
Wuhan new cases are expected at the end of March "Qingnil" when Wuhan "Qingnil," in the final analysis depends on our efforts.
如果工作抓得紧一点，而且不出现其他突发情况，比如国外输入性病例，或许武汉在三月底就能“清零”。
If the work is tight and there are no other emergencies, such as imported cases from abroad, Wuhan may be able to "clean up" by the end of March.
要严防国外输入性病例现在全国很多地区新增病例“清零”了，但千万不能麻痹大意，要严防国外输入性病例。
Foreign imports to strictly prevent cases of sexual cases in many areas of the country is now "zero", but must not be insensitive, to strictly prevent the importation of sexual cases abroad.
检测、隔离还是要做好。
Test, isolate or do a good job.
如果其他国家不重视，疫情可能在全球更大范围爆发新冠疫情是否会在全球更大范围内爆发，要看世界其他国家的防控力度。
If other countries do not pay attention, it is up to the rest of the world to determine whether a wider global outbreak of the new crown could erupt.
如果他们不重视疫情防控，不注意传染源隔离，新冠疫情将有可能在全球更大范围内爆发。
If they do not pay attention to disease prevention and control, do not pay attention to the source of infection isolation, the new crown epidemic will likely erupt on a wider global scale.
希望世界各国能够像中国这样，认真对待这次疫情。
I hope the rest of the world will take this outbreak seriously, as China has done.
进入ICU问诊是一种习惯作为医生，要真正了解患者病情，除了听汇报，自己一定要去病房看一下。
Access to ICU consultation is a habit as a doctor, to really understand the patient's illness, in addition to listening to the report, he must go to the ward to see.
病人的一切情况都要引起医生重视。
All the patient's condition should be valued by the doctor.
尤其是重症病人，许多病情的变化，如果能够在早期发现、诊断、治疗，就有可能避免转为危重症，甚至避免死亡。
In severe cases, in particular, changes in many conditions, if detected, diagnosed and treated at an early stage, are likely to avoid becoming critically ill or even dying.
一个医生一定要在病人身边，才能做出正确判断和决策。
A doctor must be close to the patient before he can make a correct judgment and decision.
“理想就是做一名好医生”从1968年成为“赤脚医生”开始，我的理想就是做一名好医生。
"The ideal is to be a good doctor" From 1968 became "barefoot doctor", my ideal is to be a good doctor.
我也是穷苦出身，没有党和人民对我的培养，就没有我的今天。
I was also born poor, without the party and the people of my training, I do not have today.
所以，我立志此生要做一点有益于人民的事。
Therefore, I am determined to do something beneficial to the people in this life.
减轻病人痛苦，挽救病人生命，是我一辈子最大的追求。
To alleviate the suffering of patients and save their lives is the greatest pursuit of my life.
